  "response": "Identifying the \"best\" cardiologist in Delhi can be subjective as it depends on specific patient needs, personal experiences, and various criteria such as expertise, specialty, reputation, and patient reviews. However, some of the highly reputed cardiologists in Delhi include:\n\n1. **Dr. Ashok Seth** - Chairman of Fortis Escorts Heart Institute and one of the foremost experts in the field.\n2. **Dr. Naresh Trehan** - Chairman and Managing Director of Medanta - The Medicity, well-known for his surgical skills and leadership.\n3. **Dr. Ajay Kaul** - Chairman of the Cardiac Sciences Department at BLK Super Specialty Hospital.\n4. **Dr. T.S. Kler** - Executive Director at the Heart Institute, Cardiology at Fortis Escorts Heart Institute.\n5. **Dr. Balbir Singh** - Chairman of Cardiology - Pan Max Hospitals, known for his expertise in electrophysiology.\n\nPatients are encouraged to do thorough research, read reviews, consult multiple experts, and consider credentials and second opinions before deciding on a cardiologist.",
